rows.label: bf11500150_0060
rows.name:
Hey, you! You wouldn't be Ornella-san's
former Blade, would you?

rows.label: bf11500150_0080
rows.name: From the Territorial Defense Corps! It is you!

rows.label: bf11500150_0100
rows.name:
Ooh, I remember 'em well!
Even though I was knee-high to a grasshopper back then...

rows.label: bf11500150_0110
rows.name:
With that sword slung across your back...
You were so cool.

rows.label: bf11500150_0120
rows.name:
If you hadn't come when you did,
our village would've been...

rows.label: bf11500150_0135
rows.name:
The house you used to live in
is still out there on the outskirts.

rows.label: bf11500150_0175
rows.name: I heard it's been 90 years, but...

rows.label: bf11500150_0180
rows.name:
What is it?
Did you remember something?

rows.label: bf11500150_0200
rows.name:
Really? That's too bad.
I would've liked to have learned about the old you.

rows.label: bf11500150_0210
rows.name:
I am...who I am.
I do not change.

rows.label: bf11500150_0240
rows.name: Ugh... You got me right here...

rows.label: bf11500150_0270
rows.name: That! That was such an awesome line!

rows.label: bf11500150_0290
rows.name:
Shin you didn't even realize, did you?
Sometimes you'll...say something, and I'll just swoon.

rows.label: bf11500150_0310
rows.name: I don't think any girl could refuse you.

rows.label: bf11500150_0330
rows.name: Nuh-uh, you're smooth and you know it.

rows.label: bf11500150_0370
rows.name: Y-yes... Yes, I think it is.

rows.label: bf11500150_0380
rows.name:
Standing next to you,
with such a goofy blissful smile?

rows.label: bf11500150_0385
rows.name: It has to be, I'm sure of it.

rows.label: bf11500150_0400
rows.name:
Hey.
We should take a photo.
